title: 235 - Two Kittens
description:
Have you ever hired a coach or taken advice from someone you trusted and didn't get the results you wanted? You did everything they told you to do; you took the course, read the book, yet you're still in the same place. On today's podcast, the guys talk about what it takes to get real sustained, permanent change in your life—a change in behavior, and your mindset will lead to the results you want.
 The Secret to Success Topics:
  [04:00] - Trey’s Comedy Corner
 [07:00] - West Coast E
 [23:30] - Results
 [30:40] - The Big Gig
 [40:00] - Perspective Shift
 [51:28] - Guard The Mind
 [1:13:00] - Windows Closing
  The Secrets 2 Success:
  You can’t talk yourself into something you behaved yourself into.
 Talking doesn’t change it, you have to work on your behavior.
 Change your perspective on things so you can do them better.
 It’s not who you are that holds you back, it's who you think you’re not.
